description: The RAF cargo plane became the largest aircraft to touch down on the island as it took part in training.
title: Largest ever plane landed at Guernsey Airport by Royal Air Force
title_page: Largest ever plane landed at Guernsey Airport by Royal Air Force - BBC News
maintext: He added: "There are also many less civilian aircraft flying at the moment so the availability of civil airfields for our training is much greater than normal."
